{
  "stem": "13313.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he walks towards the major street that had been the major Jewish street in the Jewish district, in the area where we had been taking those letters.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And passed that area where I had seen that truck and those Germans pick up the people on the street.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he turns the corner into the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Any Jew from Antwerp or people who have to know the [NON-ENGLISH] is that-- is the street that was a Jewish area.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was going to say, almost like here, Battery Street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And he-- and he walks in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he's halfway on the block.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I jump this kid with every possible rage that I had in me.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I jump this kid and I start pummelling him, and kicking him, and beating him up.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now, if he had just turned around and given me one swat, he would have just-- I was just-- but he didn't know what hit him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And he got-- and he was really-- and he started to sob and cry.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was-- my feud-- he finally got out from under and he, and he took off.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And he-- I felt very, very good.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Very good that I hadn't, had faced it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was this experience.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the reason I, I, I bring this up was that we were just liberated, and you have to hear this again.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, the antisemitism, race hatred, you name it, even to this day, all over the world, has been going on ever since.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The issue has not gone away in the minds of the people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But it started even right then, right after the liberation.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, what happened was that, as I said-- by the way, my father escaped from this train to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
